quran[6{c,v,t}:
13,43,"yeh munkareen kehte hain ke tum khuda ke beje hue nahi ho kaho"" mere aur tumahray darmain Allah ki gawahi kaafi hai aur phir har uss shakhs ki gawahi jo kitaab aasmani ka ilm rakhta hai """
14,1,"alif -lam-ra ,ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, yeh aik kitaab hai jis ko hum ne tumhari taraf nazil kya hai taakay tum logon ko tarikeon se nikaal kar roshni mein lao, un ke rab ki tofeq se, uss khuda ke rastay par jo zabardast aur apni zaat mein aap Mahmood hai"
14,2,aur zameen aur asmano ki saari mojoodaat ka maalik hai aur sakht tabah kin saza hai qubool haq se inkaar karne walon ke liye
14,3,"jo duniya ki zindagi ko akhirat par tarjeeh dete hain, jo Allah ke rastay se logon ko rok rahay hain aur chahtay hain ke yeh rasta ( un ki khwahisaat ke mutabiq ) terah ho jaye yeh log gumraahi mein bohat daur nikal gay hain"
14,4,"hum ne apna pegham dainay ke liye jab kabhi koi rasool bheja hai, uss ne apni qoum hi ki zabaan mein pegham diya hai taakay woh inhen achi terhan khol kar baat samjhaye phir Allah jisay chahta hai bhatka deta hai aur jisay chahta hai hadaayat bakhshta hai, woh baala dast aur hakeem hai"
14,5,hum iss se pehlay moose ko bhi apni nishanion ke sath bhaij chuke hain usay bhi hum ne hukum diya tha ke apni qoum ko tarikeon se nikaal kar roshni mein laa aur inhen tareekh Ellahi ke sabaq amooz waqeat suna kar nasiyaat kar inn waqeat mein barri nishanain hain har uss shakhs ke liye jo sabr aur shukar karne wala ho
